    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月ストがBIG4になってしばらく経った頃",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n今日の収録は長丁場でしたね",
      "startTime": 5.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。しかし三本録りの予定が\n急遽一本増えるとは思わなかったよ",
      "startTime": 12.1999993007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "疲れているところ悪いんだが、帰る前に\n明日の予定をもう一度確認しておこうか",
      "startTime": 18.033332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "午前中にライブの打ち合わせ、午後にラジオ収録と\nインタビュー、それから特番のゲスト出演ですよね",
      "startTime": 25.6666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "今までもそれなりに忙しくさせてもらってると思って\nましたけど……BIG4になった影響は大きいですね",
      "startTime": 34.233332634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "朝から分刻みのスケジュールだけど、大丈夫か？\nさすがに休む時間が少な過ぎるよな",
      "startTime": 43.2666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。仕事を受けるかどうかは毎回確認を\nとってくれてるじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 50.6199106369,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_09_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "それに、サニピがBIG4になった時の目の回るような\n忙しさを目の前で見てましたから。想定内です",
      "startTime": 57.3666659673,
      "sfxList": []
    }
